                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen combined heat and power generation optimization scheduling method and system for regional heating",
                    "一种用于区域供暖的氢热电联产优化调度方法及系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a hydrogen heat and power cogeneration optimization scheduling method for regional heating, and the method comprises the following steps: building a thermal load prediction model for regional heating, predicting the thermal load according to historical data and real-time data, and forming a real-time thermal load curve; hydrogen production, hydrogen-to-electricity conversion, hydrogen combustion, heat pumps and peripheral fire coal or traditional unit multi-heat sources are configured; designing an optimal scheduling model for each heat source by adopting a DDPG depth deterministic strategy gradient algorithm according to a thermal load demand predicted in real time, and solving an optimal load distribution mode and control parameters; according to the control parameters and the heat source utilization priorities, dynamically adjusting multiple heat sources so as to reduce the dependence of regional heating on fossil energy; on the basis of an intelligent algorithm, the heat consumption load is predicted in real time, and multiple heat sources are intelligently regulated and controlled, so that the hydrogen energy utilization rate and the heating efficiency are improved while the heat consumption requirement of a real-time heat load curve is met, and the heat supply amount of a traditional regional heating coal-fired unit is reduced or even replaced; and low-carbon, high-efficiency and intelligent regional heating is realized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种用于区域供暖的氢热电联产优化调度方法，包括以下步骤：建立区域供暖的热负荷预测模型，根据历史数据和实时数据对热负荷进行预测，并形成实时热负荷曲线；配置制氢、氢转电、燃氢、热泵及周边燃煤或传统机组多方热源；根据实时预测的热负荷需求，采用DDPG深度确定性策略梯度算法设计对各个热源的优化调度模型，求解最优的负荷分配方式及控制参数；根据控制参数和热源利用优先级，对多方热源进行动态调节，以减少区域供暖对化石能源的依赖；基于本发明通过智能算法对用热负荷实时预测以及对多方热源进行智能调控，使其满足实时热负荷曲线的用热需求的同时提高氢能利用率和供暖效率，减少甚至替换传统区域供暖的燃煤机组的供热量，实现区域供暖的低碳化、高效化和智能化。"
                }
            ]
